title: Executive Navigator Watch Face
summary: A relic of the seas, complete with all accurate to the millisecond hands.
description: A touch of excellence. This watchface will enrich any smartwatch with a full, finely formed design.  It features an image of a ship along side an old-styled compass.  A true naval relic.The hands move by the millisecond to get the most accurate and smooth experience.this gold and silver watch displays the day of the week and the date as an added watch complication.Once downloaded, this watch face will be available in the Android Wear app. It may take a few minutes for the watchface to appear in the selection menu. If it does not, then go to the Settings menu of the Android Wear app and tap on Resync Apps.This app was tested on the Moto 360 and Sony Smartwatch 3.  However, it will work on most android wear smartwatches.
descriptionHTML:
A touch of excellence. This watchface will enrich any smartwatch with a full, finely formed design. It features an image of a ship along side an old-styled compass. A true naval relic.
The hands move by the millisecond to get the most accurate and smooth experience.
this gold and silver watch displays the day of the week and the date as an added watch complication.

Once downloaded, this watch face will be available in the Android Wear app. It may take a few minutes for the watchface to appear in the selection menu. If it does not, then go to the Settings menu of the Android Wear app and tap on Resync Apps.

This app was tested on the Moto 360 and Sony Smartwatch 3. However, it will work on most android wear smartwatches.
comments: Beautiful on the Moto 360 Had to uninstall, reinstall to make it work, but after that....live it. Beautiful.
Waste of money. This app wouldn't sync with my Moto 360, or with Android Wear, no matter what I've tried...
